Package gameClient.Game_DS

Class Agents

java.lang.Object
gameClient.Game_DS.Agents
public class Agents
extends java.lang.Object
Represents the list of the game's Agents.

game - the game server. info - the game's information. agents - the game's Agents. dps - a matrix holds the shortest paths between a node to any other node.

Author:
Shaked Aviad & Rotem Halbreich
